    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casa Caballero is a single-player, first-person survival horror game set in a fictional area in the Philippines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your colleagues failed to return from their assignment, you are tasked to look for them in a house filled with secrets and with a resident that seems to force its visitors to stay for good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702590/extras/75c31d9e497437fe7f3535efb87005f9.poster.avif?t=1752948452\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702590/extras/75c31d9e497437fe7f3535efb87005f9.webm?t=1752948452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702590/extras/75c31d9e497437fe7f3535efb87005f9.mp4?t=1752948452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the mysteries of Casa Caballero and its residents through notes scattered across the property. Keep your eyes open for clues and items to solve puzzles and unlock new areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702590/extras/824b11f4b9b77b84a585429762f788cd.poster.avif?t=1752948452\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702590/extras/824b11f4b9b77b84a585429762f788cd.webm?t=1752948452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702590/extras/824b11f4b9b77b84a585429762f788cd.mp4?t=1752948452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with only a pistol, you must fight off the horrors lurking in the house while evading those that cannot be killed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702590/extras/9ae9a66a3d7a3bdc5718fdda5d3cf70e.poster.avif?t=1752948452\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702590/extras/9ae9a66a3d7a3bdc5718fdda5d3cf70e.webm?t=1752948452\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702590/extras/9ae9a66a3d7a3bdc5718fdda5d3cf70e.mp4?t=1752948452\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for an immersive experience that will test your problem-solving skills so you can escape Casa Caballero in one piece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic Graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging puzzle-solving</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Occasional first-person shooting</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Setting and story inspired by Philippine history, culture, and folklore</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The approximate duration of the game is 60-90mins.</strong></p>",
